text: Ordered one peanuts pancake at $1.50. It tasted plain, as it lacked fragrant and flavour, but the peanut filling was generous. Overall, average pancake.

It was ok. Was expecting much sweeter pancake. Ordered peanuts and red beans. There were 3 fillings, I forgot what was the other one.

Each pancake $1.1. Reasonable for snack price and after lunch snack. It was ready food already.
Loving their peanut pancake, filled with lots of peanuts inside! Hard to find traditional pancake in Singapore & price are still reasonable from a coffee shop. Keep up the good work üëç
